        "title": "Anderson Island Health: Community-Focused Healthcare & Wellness Services",
        "meta_descr": "Anderson Island Health offers accessible, community-focused healthcare. Explore wellness programs, affordable plans, and vital support services. Discover how we're building a mobile health hub for island residents.",
